urls.title: Long-Haul COVID-19 Symptoms May Appear in This Order
urls.description: A new poll finds that there may be a specific order for long-term COVID-19 symptoms. Flu-like symptoms, including fatigue, headache, fever, and chills, are often the first symptoms to emerge.
